    {
      "chinese": "「Taromak」族人祈雨典禮就在大南溪舉行，這裡有魚類、蝦、螃蟹、鰻魚、還有兩旁山上的植物和動物，是族人採野菜和獵人打獵的地方。感謝造天地的神賜與流奶與蜜之地。",
      "ab": "lo moriyodalre kai cekele Taromak yakaita Kadrakerara asalisi, makala ka lrakaang, a’ase, tarasorodro, tolra, maecebe legelege makala ka raceve si golragolray, takilacelacenga, tatokakaanga, tatokotokola ki lraswalralray, kai Kadrakerara mathariri ’aramoro, ataromara ki Twaomase tawthebetheba ka daeda’e.",
      "order": "3",
